==English==

===Pronunciation===
*IPA: //naʂonalizm/
*AHD: //năshŏnălĭzm/

===Etymology===
[[national]] + [[ism]]

===Noun===
'''nationalism'''
# Supporting a national identity when it does not exist as a sovereign nation.
#:''Example'' [[w:Basque nationalism|Basque nationalism]], Kurdish nationalism.
# [[jingoism]]. The support of one [[nation]] interests to the exclusion of others.
# [[patriotism]].

